					Synalloy Metals is a wholly owned subsidiary of Synalloy Corporation.  Synalloy Metals is comprised of three operating divisions that supply products and services to power, pulp and paper, petro-chemical, water/wastewater, food and beverage, chemical, OEM, pharmaceutical, clean water technology, micro-electronics, metals/steel, mining, heavy manufacturing and related industries.
Select a link below to learn more about our companies.








BRISMET is a world class supplier of high nickel alloy and stainless steel welded pipe, both domestically and internationally. BRISMET produces ½" NPS to 144" NPS and up to 3" in wall thickness.
Learn More






Palmer of Texas is a leading manufacturer of fiberglass and steel liquid storage tanks and separation equipment.  Palmer produces 2’ to 29’ 9” diameter fiberglass tanks and 2’ to 21’ 6” diameter painted steel tanks.
Learn More






 

